TextBody:
Hello Mohammed,

Thank you for contacting us.

To ensure we fully understand your situation and can address your needs effectively, we kindly ask for some additional details.

 Having more information will allow us to provide you with the most accurate and efficient support.
Before we can proceed further with the case, can you please provide us the following information:

•        What is the impact of the issue on your business?

•        Who is affected by this issue?

•        What are the steps to reproduce?

•        Have you attempted any troubleshooting steps yet? If so, what have you tried?

•        What are you trying to do or accomplish?

•        When did this issue start?

•        Can you please let us know the Client, Server, OS version (if not already known) on which the situation is encountered?

•       Screen shots, logs, other artifacts, etc.
Once we have these details, we will be able to analyze the situation comprehensively and take the necessary steps to assist you further.

Best Regards,
Marian Ilies | Technical Support Engineer
Endpoint Protector by CoSoSys, now part of Netwrix

www.netwrix.com
